OL,6,FResidents on a street with 'risk to
OL,7,Flife' still have no solutions to heavy
OL,8,Fflooding - four years after hit.
OL,10,FClydach Terrace in Ynysybwl, , was
OL,11,Fbadly hit in February 2020 when the
OL,12,FRiver Taff burst its banks and quickly
OL,13,Fflooded homes.
OL,15,FPaul Thomas, who has called the road
OL,16,Fhome for more than 40 years, describes
OL,17,Fthe moment disaster struck.
