OL,6,FHe told ITV's : "It was horrendous. On
OL,7,Fthe night that it happened I spent an
OL,8,Fhour plus trying to stop the water
OL,9,Fcoming into my property."
OL,11,FPaul's disabled daughter lives next
OL,12,Fdoor and was hit by the floodwater
OL,13,Ffirst. A fountain of water taller than
OL,14,Fhim was coming out of the toilet.
