OL,6,FHe said: "I tried to ram towels into
OL,7,Fthe toilet to stop it. Then I had to
OL,8,Fmake the hardest decision I've had to
OL,9,Fmake in a long time and say to my
OL,10,Fdaughter, 'get upstairs - you're on
OL,11,Fyour own, I've got to try and stop it
OL,12,Fcoming into my house'. I had to leave
OL,13,Fher with that and that was hard to
OL,14,Fdeal with."
OL,16,FDespite his best efforts, Paul's home
OL,17,Fflooded almost up to ceiling height.
OL,18,FHis family's belongings were destroyed.
