OL,6,FThe Thomas' have since renovated their
OL,7,Fhome - but they still live in fear of
OL,8,Fflooding every time it rains.
OL,10,FMr Thomas said: "I've lived here 40
OL,11,Fyears, my children were all been born
OL,12,Fhere.
OL,14,F"But living here is very hard; when
OL,15,Fwinter time comes it's an unbelievable
OL,16,Ffeeling that we get.
