OL,3,C'Every time it rains our anxiety
OL,4,Craises to a tremendous level'
OL,6,F"Every time it rains you're thinking
OL,7,F'is it going to happen tonight', you
OL,8,Fmove your stuff upstairs. My furniture
OL,9,Fhas been up and down the stairs more
OL,10,Ftimes than a sale in DFS.
OL,12,F"It's unreal to live here. We've got a
OL,13,FFacebook page and you can sense the
OL,14,Fmood. Some people get really upset
OL,15,Fwhen it rains, or if there's heavy
OL,16,Frain forecast.
OL,18,F"We've got weather alerts - they're
OL,19,Fnice - but they don't do anything for
OL,20,Fus but raise our anxiety to a
OL,21,Ftremendous level."
