OL,6,FThe authorities are drawing up a list
OL,7,Fof options of what to do but that
OL,8,Fcould take until the end of the decade.
OL,10,F"One option is to build a wall which
OL,11,Fwould reduce the carriageway so it
OL,12,Fwould be single file traffic and no
OL,13,Fmore parking in the street," Mr Thomas
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"If you've got a three metre wall
OL,17,Foutside your house that's going to
OL,18,Fdevalue it even more.
