OL,6,F"Another option they're considering is
OL,7,Fto take the top off the tunnel culvert
OL,8,Fat the bottom of the street - that
OL,9,Fwon't do any good because if you take
OL,10,Fthe top off you've still got the
OL,11,Fwidth. And the third option is to buy
OL,12,Fthe street out and condemn the street."
OL,14,FClydach Terrace lies on the natural
OL,15,Ffloodplain in a very constrained
OL,16,Fsection of the valley and has
OL,17,Fhistorically suffered from severe
OL,18,Fflooding.
