OL,6,F(NRW) says the community has a unique
OL,7,Fflood risk due to its position. When
OL,8,Fit floods, it does so quickly and to a
OL,9,Fgreat depth, which means there is a
OL,10,Frisk to life.
OL,12,FThere are currently no flood defences
OL,13,Fin Ynysybwl, although NRW says it
OL,14,Fcarries out regular maintenance work
OL,15,Fto manage the flood risk. NRW removed
OL,16,Fmore than 700 tonnes of river shoal
OL,17,Fmaterial from the river channel
OL,18,Fadjacent to Clydach Terrace since 2020.
