OL,6,FClare Pillman, Chief Executive, said:
OL,7,F"These things are complex. Flooding is
OL,8,Fsomething that, increasingly, we're
OL,9,Flearning to live with and, as we saw
OL,10,Fduring Storm Dennis, particularly in
OL,11,Fthese short, flashy catchments the
OL,12,Frivers rise very quickly, the flood
OL,13,Fplain has been built on and there is
OL,14,Fnowhere easy for the water to go.
OL,16,F"What we don't want to do is build
OL,17,Fsomething that will work for one
OL,18,Fcommunity's challenges but puts
OL,19,Fanother community at greater risk."
